As the Chief Medical Officer, create specific task assignments for the specialist team based on your analysis.

Query: What's my cholesterol trend over the last 15 years? I want to see trends across the top 4 cholesterol metrics including Triglycerides across that time period (standard)
Complexity: STANDARD
Your Analytical Approach: **Data Points for Investigation:**
- Extract actual values and dates for all cholesterol measurements (HDL, LDL, Triglycerides)
- Retrieve Total Cholesterol data (may need alternative search terms)
- Consolidate the two different triglyceride data sets (uppercase vs. standard case)
